config KCRYPT
    tristate "kcrypt: AES-ECB Kernel Crypto Module using kchunk"
    depends on KCHUNK
    default m
    help
      Enables the kcrypt kernel module, which performs AES-ECB
      encryption and decryption using the in-kernel crypto API
      and a custom chunk-based allocator (kchunk). Intended for
      controlled heap allocation and crypto operation experiments.